{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}Hello HomeController!{% endblock %}

{% block body %}

<div class="homeBackground">

    <h1>Bienvenue sur Wakfu Tournament</h1><br>

    <div class="newContent">
        <h2>News du moment</h2>

        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Quisque rutrum eros nibh, venenatis tristique neque dignissim vel. Morbi rutrum orci in tortor ultrices, in feugiat arcu tincidunt. In iaculis vulputate tincidunt. Suspendisse semper odio non dolor pharetra, eget molestie libero tincidunt. Nam molestie orci metus, eget interdum urna euismod at. Duis ipsum nisi, venenatis at libero in, vestibulum feugiat sem. Etiam imperdiet magna sit amet tortor sodales, sit amet condimentum odio pellentesque. Ut vitae lectus blandit, aliquam erat nec, rhoncus mauris. Donec finibus nibh a urna dapibus, a porta dolor mattis.</p>

    </div>

    <div class="slideShowTournament">

        <h2>prochain tournois pr√©vus</h2>
        
        <div class="slider">
    
            {% for tournament in tournaments %}
    
                {% if date(tournament.startDate) > date('d') %} 
    
                <div class="mySlides">
    
                    <figure>
                        <img src="{{ asset('img/user/tournament/' ~ tournament.imgTournament) }}" alt="Logo du tournois">
                    </figure>
    
                    <div>
    
                        <p class="slideTournamentName">{{tournament.tournamentName}}</p>
    
                        <div class="slideTournamentInfo">
                            <p>du {{tournament.startDate | date('d-m-Y')}} au {{tournament.endDate | date('d-m-Y')}}</p>
                            <p>sur {{tournament.server}}</p>
                        </div>
    
                    </div>
    
                </div>
    
                {% endif %}
            
            {% endfor %}
    
            <button class="slideButton left-button" onclick="plusDivs(-1)">&#10094;</button>
            <button class="slideButton right-button" onclick="plusDivs(+1)">&#10095;</button>
    
        </div>

    </div>

    


</div>
{% endblock %}

{% block javascripts %}
    <script src="{{ asset('js/menuBurger.js') }}"></script>
    <script src="{{ asset('js/slideShow.js') }}"></script>
{% endblock %}
